rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! You showed up at
just the right time!

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0002
rows.name:
You already know that the Invidian
Divine Beast swallows down stuff from
the outside now and again, right?

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, you should know.
You're some of the stuff
it swallowed, aincha?

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0004
rows.name:
That's exactly what I
wanted to ask you about.

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0005
rows.name:
I need you to go check if
anything dangerous washed
up with all that junk.

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0009
rows.name:
If you do find something dodgy, don't
touch it. It might be hazardous.

rows.label: tlk43320242_06_msg0010
rows.name:
Just let me know about
it if you find some.
